  "description": "<p>网店售卖“代看望老人”服务可陪聊、陪购、陪出游，记者于上周在网上订购1小时，全程体验网店店主到安老院代看望老人，上门服务、按时计费，老人感动、买家实惠，看似皆大欢喜。&#160; 不过，昨日记者回访时意外发现<strong>，此前接受“快递孝心”的林阿姨坦言，代看望服务贴心，但“服务员”走后心里更加失落，心中除了对孩子的渴盼，又徒增对陌生人带来惊喜的渴盼；而网店店主则感叹赚了人气不赚钱，因此无奈于昨日暂停此业务。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2eb7df24/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244874.htm&amp;t=%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E8%B4%AD1%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E2%80%9C%E5%AD%9D%E5%BF%83%E2%80%9D+%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%90%8E%E9%9A%BE%E5%BF%8D%E8%90%BD%E5%B7%AE%E5%80%8D%E6%84%9F%E5%AF%82%E5%AF%9E\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244874.htm&amp;t=%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E8%B4%AD1%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E2%80%9C%E5%AD%9D%E5%BF%83%E2%80%9D+%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%90%8E%E9%9A%BE%E5%BF%8D%E8%90%BD%E5%B7%AE%E5%80%8D%E6%84%9F%E5%AF%82%E5%AF%9E\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244874.htm&amp;t=%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E8%B4%AD1%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E2%80%9C%E5%AD%9D%E5%BF%83%E2%80%9D+%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%90%8E%E9%9A%BE%E5%BF%8D%E8%90%BD%E5%B7%AE%E5%80%8D%E6%84%9F%E5%AF%82%E5%AF%9E\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244874.htm&amp;t=%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E8%B4%AD1%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E2%80%9C%E5%AD%9D%E5%BF%83%E2%80%9D+%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%90%8E%E9%9A%BE%E5%BF%8D%E8%90%BD%E5%B7%AE%E5%80%8D%E6%84%9F%E5%AF%82%E5%AF%9E\" target=\"_blank\"><img bord